snippet.title: Nuvoid Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Nuvoid, a free roam 3D space adventure where you get to build your very own ships from scratch.

To follow the progress of Nuvoid, make sure to subscribe, like us on twitter, or like us on facebook!
